Name: Announcements
Description: Naomi makes announcements at scheduled times.

Name: Archive Audiolog
Description: Allows the user to export their audiolog database and audio files into an archive file that can be merged into a different Naomi using the Import Audiolog plugin.

Name: Chuck Norris Jokes
Description: Have Naomi tell random Chuck Norris Jokes

Name: Control LED
Description: A simple module that combines Naomi and the Arduino platform to show possibilities in IOT and new interactions.

Name: Deep Speech
Description: Speech-To-Text implementation which relies on the DeepSpeech api

Name: Facebook Birthdays
Description: Keep track of Facebook friends' birthdays

Name: frotz
Description: Would you like to play a game?

Name: Google AIY Voice V1 Visualizations
Description: Visualizations of Naomi's internal state for the Google AIY Voice V1 kit

Name: googlecalendar
Description: Set and retrieve events from your Google calendar

Name: Import Audiolog
Description: Allows the user to import and merge an audiolog archive created by the Archive Audiolog plugin.

Name: NetworkCheck
Description: Simple speechhandler plugin, tells if it is connected to a network and what its IP Address is.

Name: NWS Weather
Description: Get weather forecasts for US locations from the US National Weather Service.

Name: Pocketsphinx_KWS
Description: Keyword recognizer that uses threshold confidence values to match a few words. When combined with a personalized acoustic model, this works reasonably well.
